cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use SoviaMate in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "SoviaMate: Toward End-to-End Spoken Dialogue Systems"
abstract: "An open research project building toward end-to-end spoken dialogue systems. The current release ships a neural audio codec designed for LLM integration, featuring an ASR decoder before quantization, continuous features for LLM input, enhancement-based training, and post-quantization zero-shot speaker adaptation."
